    "custom_liquid_8K9KGC": {
      "type": "custom-liquid",
      "custom_css": [
        ".private .white-label-form,.distributor .form-distributors {display: block;}",
        ".form-container {max-height: 85dvh; overflow: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; scrollbar-color: #00000025 transparent;}",
        ".close {position: absolute; top: 30px; right: 30px; width: 28px; height: 28px; display: flex; justify-content: center; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 500; padding-left: 1px; align-items: center; background: #fff; border-radius: 50%; cursor: pointer;}"
      ],
      "name": "t:sections.custom-liquid.presets.name",
      "settings": {
        "custom_liquid": "<div class=\"portal\">\n  <div class=\"portal-container\">\n    <span class=\"close\">⨉</span>\n\n    {% render 'distributor-form' %}\n    {% render 'private-form' %}\n\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<script>\ndocument.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {\n\n  const portal = document.querySelector('#shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .portal');\n  const closeBtn = document.querySelector('#shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .close');\n  const portalContainer = portal.querySelector('.portal-container');\n\n  closeBtn.addEventListener('click', () => {\n    portal.className = 'portal';\n  });\n\n  ['distributor', 'private'].forEach(type => {\n    const button = document.querySelector(`a[href=\"#${type}\"]`);\n\n    if (!button) return;\n\n    button.addEventListener('click', e => {\n      e.preventDefault();\n\n      portal.className = 'portal';\n      portal.classList.add(type);\n    });\n  });\n\n  document.addEventListener('click', e => {\n    if (portal.className === 'portal') return;\n\n    if (\n      portal.contains(e.target) &&\n      !portalContainer.contains(e.target)\n    ) {\n      portal.className = 'portal';\n    }\n  });\n\n});\n\ndocument.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {\n\n  const submittedForm = sessionStorage.getItem('submittedForm');\n\n  if (!submittedForm) return;\n\n  const portal = document.querySelector('.portal');\n\n  if (submittedForm === 'private') {\n    portal.className = 'portal private';\n\n    const success = document.querySelector('.white-label-form .form-success');\n    if (success) success.style.display = 'block';\n  }\n\n  if (submittedForm === 'distributor') {\n    portal.className = 'portal distributor';\n\n    const success = document.querySelector('.form-distributors .form-success');\n    if (success) success.style.display = 'block';\n  }\n});\n</script>\n\n<style>\n.form-container::-webkit-scrollbar {\n  width: 1px;\n  height: 1px;\n}\n\n.form-container::-webkit-scrollbar-track {\n  background: transparent;\n  border-radius: 99px;\n}\n\n.form-container::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {\n  background: #00000025;\n  border-radius: 99px;\n}\n\n.form-container::-webkit-scrollbar-button {\n  display: none;\n}\n\n.form-container::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover {\n  background: #00000030;\n}\n\n/* Popup hidden by default */\n.portal {\n  display: none;\n}\n\n/* Open popup */\n.portal.private,\n.portal.distributor {\n  display: flex;\n}\n\n/* Hide both forms by default */\n.white-label-form,\n.form-distributors {\n  display: none;\n}\n\n/* Private button => only private form */\n.portal.private .white-label-form {\n  display: block;\n}\n\n.portal.private .form-distributors {\n  display: none;\n}\n\n/* Distributor button => only distributor form */\n.portal.distributor .form-distributors {\n  display: block;\n}\n\n.portal.distributor .white-label-form {\n  display: none;\n}\n\n.portal-container {\n  width: max-content;\n  height: max-content;\n}\n</style>",
        "color_scheme": "scheme-4",
        "padding_top": 0,
        "padding_bottom": 0
      }
    },
    "multicolumn_iKA74Y": {
      "type": "multicolumn",
      "blocks": {
        "column_QWDrhH": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "title": "",
            "text": "",
            "link_label": "",
            "link": "",
            "custom_liquid": "<h2 class=\"h2\">Why <b>Us</b>?</h2>\n<p>\nHimalayan Cliff Honey is dedicated to bringing the highest quality cliff honey to the market. We monitor the entire production process since harvesting, with our team present in the harvesting site, visiting the fields to oversee the whole harvesting process. We own our private storage and packaging facilities, where all the steps from processing to final packaging are conducted following the highest international quality and safety standards.\n</p>\n<p>\nBesides working in close terms with the local honey hunter community and bringing raw, authentic honey to the market, every batch of our production is also tested in an internationally accredited laboratory, which provides a solid verification of the nutritional content and purity. Also, we provide a vertically integrated service helping turn your vision into reality so that your idea of a private label brand is crafted and further nurtured to meet the highest international standards, from initial concept to a trusted global brand.\n</p>\n\n<p>\nHimalayan Cliff Honey is proud to be one of the highest Himalayan cliff honey collectors and distributors in Nepal. Our flexibility in wholesale and private label services guarantees we serve our role as a credible supplier of authentic cliff honey to retailers and suppliers.\n</p>\n<h3>Honey Production</h3>\n<p>\nHimalayan Cliff Honey is a natural product of Nepal, one of the countries popular for producing exquisite and distinctive ”mad honey”. We serve as a trusted supplier of the best quality Himalayan cliff honey to customers worldwide and also offer wholesale and private-label services globally. The cliff honey is renowned for its unique psychedelic effects and medicinal properties.\n</p>\n<a class=\"button\" href=\"/contact\" >Contact Us</a>"
          }
        },
        "column_h66fjY": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "title": "",
            "text": "",
            "link_label": "",
            "link": "",
            "custom_liquid": "<h3>Creating your brand to meet your Business and Market Needs</h3>\n\n<p>\nWhether you’ve an existing or new business concept in mind, we offer full-service solutions- from product development and label design to exporting directly to your doorstep. We have developed a flexible and fully customized approach to give a unique identity to your business and meet your specific market requirements.\n</p>\n<p>\nThe premium batches of honey and all our products are ready and available for you. Simply reach out to us, and our dedicated team members will guide you to bring your finished product to the market in the best and highest quality possible.\n</p>\n<h3>Craftsmen of Mad Honey</h3>\n\n<p>\nOur brand products are solely a gift from the heart of Nepal, brought to you by native harvesters, a skilled group who have crafted and excelled in all the harvesting techniques. Their expertise is not gained overnight; they have met every misstep, every near miss, and every small failure with patience and perseverance, gradually turning into mastery over time.\n</p>\n<p>\nThe generation-old techniques have multiple benefits, ensuring the honey remains the purest form of nature’s gift. The product is even certified by the Nepal Government and tested in internationally recognised laboratories.\n</p>\n<p>\nWe act as a partner that helps your brand succeed with this world-class Himalayan cliff honey. With us, be confident in sourcing, customised packaging, and any other services that you’ve envisioned.\n</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "column_QWDrhH",
        "column_h66fjY"
      ],
