          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Do you offer wholesale Himalayan Cliff Honey for bulk purchase?",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>Yes. We also bulk supply Himalayan Cliff Honey to retailers, importers, private-label brands, and hospitality businesses across markets worldwide. Products are available in multiple bulk formats suitable for food service, retail repacking, and further processing. Contact our dedicated B2B team with your wholesale inquiries to discuss the volume, destination market, and regulatory requirements.</p>",
