          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_t9737M": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What is the minimum order quantity for any wholesale orders?",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>Minimum order quantities vary depending on the product format you choose and destination market.</p><ul><li>Bulk raw honey orders generally start from 60 kg.</li><li>Private label orders with custom packaging come with varying thresholds depending on branding complexity.</li></ul><p>Final MOQs are confirmed after reviewing order details and compliance needs.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_ibVWn8": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Do you provide private label and white label honey services?",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>Yes. We offer private and white label solutions for businesses seeking origin-verified honey under their own brand. Services include:</p><ul><li>Custom jar sizes and packaging formats</li><li>Label and packaging customization</li><li>Regulatory and export documentation support</li></ul><p>Production is managed from sourcing through final packaging to ensure consistency and compliance.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_yYheHd": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What certifications and quality testing does your honey have?",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>Each batch is tested by Nepal government-approved laboratories and independent third-party labs. Testing includes purity verification, moisture content, and authenticity parameters. We provide:</p><ul><li>Certificates of Analysis (COA)</li><li>Phytosanitary certificates</li><li>Country-of-origin documentation</li><li>Export clearance documentation</li><li>QR-based traceability data is available upon request.</li></ul>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_bnKk6T": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Can you create custom packaging and branding for our honey products?",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>Yes. We provide full packaging customization, including jar type, size, labeling, and secondary packaging. Our production partners accommodate retail-ready formats for specialty stores, gift sets, and food service applications. Share your brand guidelines including target retail presentation, and we'll provide mockups and pricing for your private label program.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_46JNmR": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Which countries do you export to and how is shipping handled?",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>We export to North America, Europe, Australia, the Middle East, and Asia. For shipments, we coordinate with established freight partners to support end-to-end logistics- prepared with complete export documentation and food-grade compliance. We are also flexible to coordinate with the buyer’s freight forwarder or recommend logistics partners experienced in honey and food product transportation. Shipping timelines and costs are determined by destination and order size.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_hafFtE": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What are the requirements needed to become a distributor or wholesale partner?",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>We work with registered distributors, importers, and retailers with established market presence. Requirements include:</p><ul><li>Valid business registration</li><li>Relevant import licenses</li><li>Demonstrated distribution capability in the target market</li></ul><p>Applicants must submit company details, target market information, and estimated annual volumes for evaluation.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_Kp3GPD": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Why should B2B buyers choose Himalayan Cliff Honey as their supplier?",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>We aim to provide direct access to one of the world’s rarest honeys to limited buyers. Our supply model is designed to ensure:</p><ul><li>Consistent supply of export-grade honey</li><li>Verified quality testing and compliance documentation</li><li>Flexible wholesale and private-label programs</li><li>Transparent sourcing and batch traceability</li><li>Dedicated B2B account support</li></ul><p>Our focus is on reliability, compliance, and long-term supply partnerships.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        }
      },
